        "markdown_formatted": "## Meeting Purpose\n\n[Sync on content production, blockers, and team transition.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=80.0)\n\n## Key Takeaways\n\n  - [**Team Transition:** Vivek Shankar becomes the primary POC for Prophecy, with Ehtisham Hussain shifting to a content-only role.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=80.0)\n  - [**Critical Blocker:** GrowthX needs GA4 & GSC access to build Looker dashboards for performance tracking, a key deliverable for Prophecy leadership.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=193.0)\n  - [**Production Acceleration:** Cody will publish articles immediately to bypass internal review delays, editing live copy if needed to maintain momentum.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=327.0)\n  - [**Holiday Push:** The team is front-loading content production to build a buffer before the late-December holiday break.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=295.0)\n\n## Topics\n\n### Team Transition\n\n  - [Vivek Shankar is transitioning to the primary POC role for Prophecy over the next two weeks.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=80.0)\n  - [Ehtisham Hussain will move to a content-only production role.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=80.0)\n  - [Vivek will lead all future strategy and analytics discussions.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=387.0)\n\n### Production & Process\n\n  - [**Content Status:**](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=120.0)\n      - [3 articles are in \"Ready to Publish\" (staging blocked by heavy Webflow traffic).](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=120.0)\n      - [11 articles are in \"For Review.\"](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=139.0)\n  - [**Process Improvement:**](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=327.0)\n      - [Cody will publish articles immediately to bypass internal review delays.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=327.0)\n      - [Rationale \u2192 This ensures a consistent publication cadence and prevents content from stalling.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=327.0)\n      - [Cody will edit live copy post-publication if needed.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=327.0)\n  - [**Holiday Buffer:**](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=295.0)\n      - [The team is accelerating production to build a content buffer before the late-December holiday break.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=295.0)\n      - [Ehtisham is ideating new topics, including a series on \"data transformation.\"](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=295.0)\n\n### Blockers & Resolutions\n\n  - [**Blocker: GA4 & GSC Access**](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=193.0)\n      - [**Impact:** Prevents GrowthX from building Looker dashboards for performance tracking.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=387.0)\n      - [**Status:** Prophecy IT has not yet granted access, despite escalation from Will. Cody is also blocked from viewing data.](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=193.0)\n  - [**Resolution: `/guides` Page Live**](https://fathom.video/share/kzc1gfto-Vk753uEmAs3ySET2jfoxCVT?tab=summary&timestamp=1